author: Disney
description:
The Movie Surfers are so back with “Freakier Friday.” Join the Merrell Twins, Vanessa and Veronica (@merrelltwins) for an exclusive, behind-the-scenes look at the rocking sequel to the 2003 Disney hit, “Freaky Friday.” The Movie Surfers visit the stars of the original movie, Lindsey Lohan (Anna Coleman) and Jamie Lee Curtis (Tess Coleman), and take a look back on all the antics of their original Movie Surfers episode from more than 20 years ago. The Surfers also chat with Julia Butters (Harper Coleman) and Sophia Hammons (Lily Davies) about what it’s like to act alongside the icons of the original movie and then hit red carpet for the world premiere of “Freakier Friday.” 

Watch Disney’s “Freakier Friday” in theaters Aug. 8, 2025. 

Disney’s “Movie Surfers” goes behind the scenes of Disney’s newest movies, giving fans access to exclusive interviews, red carpets, set tours, and more. The Surfers dive into the magic to discover what it takes to bring our favorite movies to life. Origina
title: Movie Surfers | Behind the Scenes of Freakier Friday
